commit_message: Fixed bamcoverage bug and updated CIPHER
Fixed bug in ATAC mode regarding peak calling not outputing correct files
Fixed bug in ATAC peak calling
Fixed bug running MACS when not using input, fixed singularity no space bug due to -c option
Fixed deeptools bamCoverage bug looking for /dev/shm outside of container
Updated CIPHER RNA-seq QoRTs stranded bug
Updated and rewrote CIPHER to use Singularity
Added in a --sample parameter to allow for choosing the number of reads to subsample
Added in --dge parameter and --smoothLen parameter for all pipelines but ATAC
Added in DESeq2 analysis for DGE
Updated help menu with new params
Added new aligner commands to all workflows
Allow user to choose from different aligners
Added docs directory for new ReadTheDocs manual
Removed default queueSize parameter from config file
Uploaded enhancer prediction model and workflow
Added --nameSorted option to QoRTS package in RNAseq workflows
Fixed bugs relating to MNase and RNA-seq workflows
Updated PE MNase-seq workflow bug dealing with incorrect chromSize file usage
Updated ChIPQC.R script, removed example data leading to aborted workflow
Added --egs and --egs_ratio parameters for low RAM systems in SE ChIPseq workflow
Removed bug in ChIPseq workflows with unavailable control bam index
Fixed bug in track generation via incorrect parameter, updated config file to only allow 5 processes at a time to reduce RAM errors
Fixed control and treat channel bug in ChIP workflow
Included --egs parameter for manually inputting effective genome size, updated RNA-seq workflows to allow for this new update, need PE RNA
Fixed bug in SE and PE RNAseq workflows regarding track generation via deeptools
Updated README, fixed bug in process_epic_effective.R
Updated all /bin files, updated README, uploaded version 1.0.0 of CIPHER to GitHub
Finished SE RNA workflow, included egs ratio parsing for SE and PE ChIP workflow
Finished PE GRO, started SE RNA workflow
Updated DNASE workflow - added coverage_generation process
Updated ChIP workflow for Pair-Ended datasets
process estimate_fragment_size now published to /fragment_sizes directory
